appeared in more than one, or I think they've all appeared in more than one,

00:03:00.639 --> 00:03:07.839
but some of these other Star Wars vehicles are similar, because someone might

00:03:07.839 --> 00:03:12.800
have not traveled in any vehicle, or they might have traveled in more than one

00:03:12.800 --> 00:03:20.320
vehicle, hopefully. So Star Wars, some fun data about the characters in the Star

00:03:20.360 --> 00:03:25.000
Wars universe, and contains some list columns to practice your list column

00:03:25.000 --> 00:03:32.279
skills on. The other new dataset is this dataset about storms in the

00:03:32.279 --> 00:03:39.759
Atlantic. This contains a whole bunch of data from the, I've forgotten where it's from,

00:03:39.759 --> 00:03:45.199
hopefully the documentation will tell me, from the NOAA Atlantic hurricane

