00:26:00.160 --> 00:26:06.400
code that you've created by copying and pasting into a function. But this is hard because

00:26:06.400 --> 00:26:12.640
dplyr lacks a property called referential transparency. So let me try and just describe

00:26:12.640 --> 00:26:19.400
this quickly. So basically, and I've created two simple functions, one that just multiplies

00:26:19.400 --> 00:26:23.800
